content:
The accounts payable balance as at 30 September 2022 mainly entailed consulting fees to 企業管理諮詢公司 of CNY2.3M and professional fees to 信用中和會計師事務所(特殊普通合夥) of CNY14.0K

SUMMARY: Used entities '企業管理諮詢公司' (CNY2.3M) and '信用中和會計師事務所(特殊普通合夥)' (CNY14.0K) which constitute significant portions of the total CNY11.8M accounts payable.
